text: Energetic materials are a class of material with high amount of stored chemical energy that can be released.https://web.archive.org/web/20110720000157/http://undergradresearch.missouri.edu/forums- conferences/abstracts/abstract-detail.php?abstractid=843 Typical classes of energetic materials are e.g. explosives, pyrotechnic compositions, propellants (e.g. smokeless gunpowders and rocket fuels), and fuels (e.g. diesel fuel and gasoline). == References ==
